headline: Analysts Raise Their Domino's Pizza Price Targets - Short 1-Month DPZ Puts for a Lower Buy-In
summary: Analysts have been raising their price targets on Domino's Pizza stock. Moreover, selling short out-of-the-money (OTM) puts in near-term expiry periods is a good play to set a lower buy-in point.
